prior to the adoption of sfas 123r, the firm used the historical volatility of its common stock price as the expected
volatility assumption in valuing options. the firm completed a review of its expected volatility assumption in 2006. effective october1, 2006, jpmorgan chase began to value its employee stock options granted or modified after that date using
